Proud father and actor Richard Mofe Damijo has taken to his Instagram to show off photos of his lookalike daughter while pointing out the resemblance. According to the veteran actor, he never saw the resemblance between him and his daughter until she pointed it out to him, saying she is his clone. In his words: “She says ‘Dad, I’m your clone’And I’m bracing up for the Christmas request but none comes. She queries ‘cant you see it?’ I smil my response. My wife says all the time that I’m the lucky one that all the kids look like me. Well, I guess I’m blessed like. proud dad Happy daughter happy father!” He wrote. Source